WEBVTT

00:00:35.930 --> 00:00:38.470
=Angels and Guards=

00:00:38.470 --> 00:00:41.310
=Episode 11=

00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:45.458
Isn't this the same scent
from the fragrance powder

00:00:46.083 --> 00:00:47.583
scattered on the ground
when we fought Diaotu?

00:00:48.541 --> 00:00:49.916
But why would

00:00:50.500 --> 00:00:51.583
a thief like Diaotu
use fragrance powder?

00:00:54.833 --> 00:00:56.791
Could it be Chang Beiming's?

00:01:11.666 --> 00:01:12.458
You want me to pay you back?

00:01:12.833 --> 00:01:13.333
No.

00:01:13.833 --> 00:01:14.416
It's for you.

00:01:19.750 --> 00:01:20.958
Soul-Stealing Fragrance.

00:01:21.250 --> 00:01:22.458
Such expensive fragrance powder.

00:01:22.791 --> 00:01:24.833
Even Hua Mange couldn't afford this.

00:01:25.500 --> 00:01:26.625
So you do know it.

00:01:28.583 --> 00:01:30.333
Why would you give

00:01:30.333 --> 00:01:31.500
a man fragrance powder?

00:01:32.333 --> 00:01:33.208
You don't wear fragrance powder?

00:01:35.166 --> 00:01:36.458
What man wears fragrance powder?

00:01:37.791 --> 00:01:38.416
Good.

00:01:42.166 --> 00:01:43.375
Why are you acting so strange today?

00:01:43.375 --> 00:01:44.083
What are you trying to say?

00:01:45.291 --> 00:01:45.750
Nothing.

00:01:46.583 --> 00:01:47.416
Men are annoying.

00:01:47.625 --> 00:01:49.041
Men who wear fragrance powder
are worse.

00:01:52.541 --> 00:01:53.125
So?

00:01:55.250 --> 00:01:56.166
So you are not annoying.

00:01:56.666 --> 00:01:57.541
Didn't you give it to me?

00:02:04.500 --> 00:02:05.375
You wore the fragrance powder?

00:02:06.125 --> 00:02:07.083
Just a little.

00:02:09.180 --> 00:02:11.390
(Yayan Rouge)

00:02:14.500 --> 00:02:16.416
(Who bought
this special fragrance powder,)

00:02:16.666 --> 00:02:17.791
(Soul-Stealing Fragrance?)

00:02:20.350 --> 00:02:22.220
(Account Book)

00:02:24.970 --> 00:02:26.583
(Purchased by Marquis Taiping's manor)

00:02:26.583 --> 00:02:27.916
(Purchased by Marquis Taiping's manor)
A maid from Marquis Taiping's manor?

00:02:34.208 --> 00:02:34.666
Bingfan.

00:02:35.416 --> 00:02:36.000
Constable Guan.

00:02:37.666 --> 00:02:38.250
Please sit.

00:02:45.625 --> 00:02:47.583
You asked us not to meet
at Chong'er Pavilion.

00:02:47.625 --> 00:02:48.833
Why bring us all the way out here?

00:02:50.500 --> 00:02:51.333
Chong'er Pavilion

00:02:51.958 --> 00:02:52.625
is too big for its own good.

00:02:53.625 --> 00:02:55.041
A man like me could never get in.

00:02:55.666 --> 00:02:56.583
They bullied you?

00:02:59.333 --> 00:02:59.708
It's fine.

00:03:00.541 --> 00:03:01.208
Let's not talk about that.

00:03:02.583 --> 00:03:03.250
Constable Guan,

00:03:03.583 --> 00:03:05.041
why are you so happy today?

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:07.916
The Jinyiwei

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:09.250
were ordered to capture Feng Fuliu.

00:03:09.500 --> 00:03:10.083
And yet,

00:03:10.416 --> 00:03:11.958
after days of waiting,
they came back empty-handed.

00:03:13.166 --> 00:03:13.916
This time,

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:15.541
our Enforcement Division
finally earned back some pride.

00:03:16.833 --> 00:03:17.958
The Jinyiwei

00:03:18.333 --> 00:03:19.708
are not so impressive after all,
are they?

00:03:22.208 --> 00:03:22.750
Constable Guan.

00:03:23.875 --> 00:03:26.208
There are three Jinyiwei
sitting right across from you.

00:03:32.791 --> 00:03:34.583
Bingfan, I didn't mean it.

00:03:37.416 --> 00:03:38.500
Then what did you mean?

00:03:38.791 --> 00:03:39.125
Forget it.

00:03:40.041 --> 00:03:40.500
Constable Guan,

00:03:41.250 --> 00:03:42.750
what did you find out for me?

00:03:44.666 --> 00:03:46.375
Ever since Marquis Taiping
was alarmed last time,

00:03:47.083 --> 00:03:48.166
Diaotu has not appeared again.

00:03:48.916 --> 00:03:51.125
I suspect Diaotu may be
in Marquis Taiping's manor

00:03:51.583 --> 00:03:54.583
and may be involved
with one of the maids.

00:03:54.958 --> 00:03:57.375
(Diaotu and a maid from the manor?)

00:03:58.166 --> 00:04:00.208
But could an ordinary maid

00:04:00.791 --> 00:04:01.958
afford fragrance powder this fine?

00:04:28.125 --> 00:04:29.666
Lu Guokai should be back by now.

00:05:17.625 --> 00:05:19.208
Catch the thief! Hurry!

00:05:20.166 --> 00:05:20.875
My lord.

00:05:22.250 --> 00:05:22.958
Get him!

00:05:25.416 --> 00:05:26.000
Chunhong?

00:05:26.125 --> 00:05:26.583
My lord.

00:05:28.250 --> 00:05:28.708
Marquis Taiping.

00:05:29.250 --> 00:05:30.625
Diaotu, the Flower-Picking Bee,

00:05:30.958 --> 00:05:32.208
has been hiding in your manor.

00:05:32.916 --> 00:05:34.416
Why is it you again?

00:05:34.625 --> 00:05:36.666
You break into my manor
at night and scheme against me.

00:05:36.666 --> 00:05:37.708
And now you say

00:05:37.708 --> 00:05:39.291
Diaotu is in my manor?

00:05:39.541 --> 00:05:40.291
Where is he?

00:05:40.291 --> 00:05:41.083
Where?

00:05:41.416 --> 00:05:42.041
That's him.

00:05:45.083 --> 00:05:46.125
Look carefully.

00:05:46.208 --> 00:05:48.958
This is my wife's maid, Chunhong.

00:05:49.208 --> 00:05:50.083
She is a woman.

00:05:50.083 --> 00:05:51.875
My lord, he is a man disguised
as a woman.

00:05:52.125 --> 00:05:53.041
Can't you see that?

00:05:53.291 --> 00:05:54.875
A man disguised as a woman?
Check it out.

00:05:55.791 --> 00:05:58.083
This is clearly my wife's maid,
Chunhong.

00:05:58.208 --> 00:05:59.875
She has been in my manor for 3 years.
Would I be wrong?

00:05:59.875 --> 00:06:02.875
She has attended to my wife closely
day and night.

00:06:03.250 --> 00:06:05.708
She has served her with the utmost care.

00:06:09.583 --> 00:06:10.541
How could this be?

00:06:13.833 --> 00:06:14.666
Was I cheated on?

00:06:14.916 --> 00:06:16.041
My lord.

00:06:17.208 --> 00:06:18.250
Right. Impossible.

00:06:18.250 --> 00:06:19.458
Impossible. It can't be.

00:06:19.833 --> 00:06:20.291
Shen Bingfan!

00:06:20.458 --> 00:06:22.000
You framed my maid.

00:06:22.291 --> 00:06:23.458
Get her!

00:06:23.583 --> 00:06:24.375
Jinyiwei on official business!

00:06:25.166 --> 00:06:26.000
Move!

00:06:26.083 --> 00:06:26.500
Surround the place.

00:06:27.208 --> 00:06:27.916
Capture Feng Fuliu.

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:28.333
Move!

00:06:29.333 --> 00:06:29.541
What...

00:06:29.708 --> 00:06:30.333
Where is Feng Fuliu?

00:06:34.333 --> 00:06:35.291
What Feng Fuliu?

00:06:35.291 --> 00:06:36.125
Where is Feng Fuliu?

00:06:36.250 --> 00:06:37.208
Are you trying to rebel?

00:06:37.583 --> 00:06:38.125
Lu Guokai!

00:06:38.125 --> 00:06:39.958
Why have you brought so many men
to my manor at night?

00:06:40.625 --> 00:06:42.000
My lord, I wouldn't dare.

00:06:42.291 --> 00:06:43.083
I received a secret report

00:06:43.291 --> 00:06:44.708
that Feng Fuliu is hiding in your manor.

00:06:45.166 --> 00:06:46.333
I was worried for your safety,

00:06:46.583 --> 00:06:47.791
so I brought the Jinyiwei
to protect you.

00:06:48.166 --> 00:06:49.666
Absurd! Absurd!

00:06:49.916 --> 00:06:50.750
First, the Flower-Picking Bee,

00:06:50.750 --> 00:06:51.625
now Feng Fuliu.

00:06:51.625 --> 00:06:52.375
What is going on?

00:06:52.500 --> 00:06:53.833
What do you take my manor for?

00:06:53.875 --> 00:06:54.708
Diaotu is here too?

00:06:55.083 --> 00:06:55.833
Where is he?

00:06:56.125 --> 00:06:56.750
Where?

00:06:58.958 --> 00:07:00.541
It's this villain disguised as a woman.

00:07:10.750 --> 00:07:11.541
Chunhong.

00:07:11.750 --> 00:07:13.541
I am Chunhong. I am Chunhong.

00:07:14.333 --> 00:07:15.416
Put your hand down. Let me see.

00:07:17.791 --> 00:07:18.333
Put it down.

00:07:19.625 --> 00:07:20.541
My lord.

00:07:20.625 --> 00:07:20.916
He...

00:07:21.041 --> 00:07:21.875
Put it down.

00:07:21.875 --> 00:07:23.458
Show them. What are you afraid of?

00:07:30.083 --> 00:07:31.791
Don't be afraid.

00:07:33.208 --> 00:07:33.958
He has an Adam's apple.

00:07:34.250 --> 00:07:35.250
He really is a man.

00:07:37.208 --> 00:07:38.791
That is disgusting.

00:07:39.500 --> 00:07:40.291
My lord.

00:07:40.666 --> 00:07:41.250
You fat pig.

00:07:41.375 --> 00:07:41.916
Get lost!

00:07:54.458 --> 00:07:54.916
Take him away!

00:07:57.250 --> 00:07:57.791
Marquis Taiping.

00:07:58.125 --> 00:07:58.750
Commissioner Lu.

00:07:59.291 --> 00:08:01.250
Would you say my gift
was generous enough?

00:08:06.916 --> 00:08:07.583
Jinyiwei, hear my order.

00:08:07.916 --> 00:08:08.375
At your command!

00:08:08.458 --> 00:08:09.458
Take men and capture Feng Fuliu.

00:08:09.541 --> 00:08:10.541
Leave Diaotu to me.

00:08:10.833 --> 00:08:11.333
Yes!

00:08:11.875 --> 00:08:12.416
Follow me!

00:08:18.750 --> 00:08:19.958
Insolent Diaotu, the Flower-Picking Bee.

00:08:20.708 --> 00:08:22.416
You assaulted countless young women

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:23.708
and have now been arrested.

00:08:24.500 --> 00:08:25.250
Do you admit your crimes?

00:08:25.583 --> 00:08:27.583
If Feng Fuliu hadn't interfered today,

00:08:28.916 --> 00:08:31.291
how could you wretched officials
have caught me?

00:08:32.125 --> 00:08:32.666
How dare you!

00:08:33.500 --> 00:08:34.750
You are on the brink of death,

00:08:35.250 --> 00:08:36.208
yet you still show no remorse.

00:08:37.583 --> 00:08:39.416
My lord, I found evidence.

00:08:43.041 --> 00:08:43.583
My lord.

00:08:43.833 --> 00:08:46.375
We found many women's clothes
in Diaotu's room,

00:08:46.583 --> 00:08:47.500
along with this fragrance powder.

00:08:48.083 --> 00:08:48.958
Soul-Stealing Fragrance.

00:08:49.500 --> 00:08:49.875
What...

00:08:52.666 --> 00:08:53.250
Commissioner Lu.

00:08:53.875 --> 00:08:55.458
This is the purchase record I found

00:08:55.458 --> 00:08:56.416
at Yayan Rouge.

00:08:59.310 --> 00:08:59.890
(Account Book)

00:09:01.041 --> 00:09:01.708
My lord, please have a look.

00:09:03.083 --> 00:09:03.541
Step back.

00:09:05.560 --> 00:09:06.520
(Purchased by a maid
from Marquis Taiping's manor)

00:09:09.833 --> 00:09:10.250
What...

00:09:10.750 --> 00:09:11.291
Guards!

00:09:11.750 --> 00:09:12.375
Take him back to the Imperial Prison

00:09:12.625 --> 00:09:13.041
to await trial.

00:09:13.375 --> 00:09:13.625
Yes!

00:09:14.291 --> 00:09:14.625
Wait.

00:09:15.583 --> 00:09:16.125
Mr. Lu.

00:09:16.541 --> 00:09:19.208
I have a few questions
to ask him in private.

00:09:20.333 --> 00:09:20.875
As you wish, my lord.

00:09:21.208 --> 00:09:21.458
Okay.

00:09:23.541 --> 00:09:24.125
Chunhong.

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:26.416
Diaotu.

00:09:27.375 --> 00:09:28.458
You spent three years in my manor.

00:09:28.833 --> 00:09:30.250
You were my wife's personal maid.

00:09:30.541 --> 00:09:31.833
You served my wife day and night.

00:09:31.833 --> 00:09:32.750
Tell me the truth.

00:09:32.750 --> 00:09:33.708
What exactly happened

00:09:33.833 --> 00:09:34.291
between you and my wife?

00:09:34.291 --> 00:09:35.250
Yin Xian, let me tell you.

00:09:35.500 --> 00:09:37.250
Your wife has been cheating on you
for ages.

00:09:37.666 --> 00:09:39.166
You are the biggest cuckold alive.

00:09:40.041 --> 00:09:41.166
I'll skin you alive!

00:09:42.125 --> 00:09:42.916
I'll skin you alive!

00:09:42.916 --> 00:09:43.458
Cuckold!

00:09:43.500 --> 00:09:44.500
I'll kill you!

00:09:44.500 --> 00:09:45.125
This is disgraceful!

00:09:45.208 --> 00:09:45.958
Guards!

00:09:46.083 --> 00:09:46.791
I'll skin you alive!

00:09:46.791 --> 00:09:47.875
Cuckold!

00:09:47.875 --> 00:09:48.625
I'll kill you!

00:09:48.791 --> 00:09:49.625
I'll kill you!

00:09:49.625 --> 00:09:51.458
Cuckold!

00:09:51.458 --> 00:09:51.958
A dignified marquis like me

00:09:52.125 --> 00:09:53.375
was cuckolded by a pervert like you!

00:09:53.375 --> 00:09:54.500
Cuckold!

00:09:54.666 --> 00:09:55.666
I was cheated on!

00:09:55.708 --> 00:09:56.125
Take him away.

00:09:56.333 --> 00:09:56.708
Yes.

00:09:56.791 --> 00:09:58.250
I'll kill you!

00:09:58.708 --> 00:09:59.541
I'll kill you!

00:09:59.541 --> 00:10:00.500
I cuckolded you!

00:10:00.875 --> 00:10:02.000
I'll kill you!

00:10:06.375 --> 00:10:06.875
Mr. Lu.

00:10:07.416 --> 00:10:08.250
In capturing Diaotu,

00:10:08.375 --> 00:10:10.250
our Enforcement Division
deserves some credit too, right?

00:10:11.416 --> 00:10:12.083
The Enforcement Division?

00:10:12.625 --> 00:10:13.541
Capturing Diaotu

00:10:13.541 --> 00:10:15.708
was all thanks to the Jinyiwei's
careful planning.

00:10:16.333 --> 00:10:17.125
What does it have to do with you?

00:10:18.250 --> 00:10:18.541
You...

00:10:19.250 --> 00:10:20.500
You can't bully your juniors like this.

00:10:21.041 --> 00:10:21.833
Guan Yunfeng.

00:10:22.500 --> 00:10:24.041
Who are you, and what rank do you hold?

00:10:24.291 --> 00:10:25.875
How dare you speak to me like that?
Step back.

00:10:30.791 --> 00:10:32.500
Why did Feng Fuliu actually show up?

00:10:36.916 --> 00:10:37.833
We failed

00:10:38.000 --> 00:10:39.166
to capture Feng Fuliu.

00:10:40.041 --> 00:10:40.625
Forget it.

00:10:41.666 --> 00:10:42.666
Chang Beiming.

00:10:58.666 --> 00:10:59.166
What are you doing?

00:11:00.625 --> 00:11:01.250
Pervert!

00:11:02.000 --> 00:11:04.041
You watched me bathe,
and I am the pervert?

00:11:07.250 --> 00:11:08.666
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

00:11:10.000 --> 00:11:10.833
Get out.

00:11:22.000 --> 00:11:22.583
(Could it be)

00:11:23.250 --> 00:11:24.416
(that he just came back too?)

00:11:27.875 --> 00:11:29.541
Were you at Chong'er Pavilion all night?

00:11:33.000 --> 00:11:34.625
I went drinking at Shizhen's place.

00:11:36.166 --> 00:11:37.416
Why are you still here?

00:11:38.041 --> 00:11:39.083
Leaving now.

00:11:40.416 --> 00:11:42.458
A man bathing
with pink flower petals.

00:11:43.791 --> 00:11:45.291
Chang Shuai even wears

00:11:45.458 --> 00:11:46.333
fragrance powder.

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:48.875
Mind your own business.

00:11:51.625 --> 00:11:52.375
This time,

00:11:52.541 --> 00:11:55.500
our Northern Bureau made a little name.

00:11:55.875 --> 00:11:57.750
I know that must upset Mr. Duan.

00:11:58.250 --> 00:11:59.625
I feel terribly guilty.

00:12:00.416 --> 00:12:02.333
You only caught Diaotu.

00:12:02.833 --> 00:12:04.250
What is so impressive about that?

00:12:04.666 --> 00:12:05.791
Well, well.

00:12:06.250 --> 00:12:08.500
Wasn't Diaotu the one

00:12:09.500 --> 00:12:11.583
who harmed your niece?

00:12:12.000 --> 00:12:14.708
Our Northern Bureau avenged her for you.

00:12:15.083 --> 00:12:16.500
At the very least,

00:12:16.916 --> 00:12:18.500
you owe me a "thank you", right?

00:12:18.875 --> 00:12:19.666
Fine.

00:12:20.583 --> 00:12:21.625
Thank you.

00:12:23.583 --> 00:12:24.333
Grand Secretary.

00:12:25.500 --> 00:12:26.916
Grand Secretary.

00:12:28.125 --> 00:12:28.833
Mr. Zhang.

00:12:28.916 --> 00:12:32.250
This time, the Jinyiwei captured Diaotu,
who terrorized the capital.

00:12:32.625 --> 00:12:33.583
His Majesty is greatly pleased.

00:12:34.250 --> 00:12:35.208
His Majesty has issued an edict

00:12:35.708 --> 00:12:36.416
commending

00:12:36.500 --> 00:12:39.875
all members of the Jinyiwei
Northern Bureau.

00:12:42.458 --> 00:12:45.541
His Majesty's grace is boundless.

00:12:46.333 --> 00:12:49.291
His Majesty's grace is boundless!

00:12:52.291 --> 00:12:53.083
Grand Secretary.

00:12:53.541 --> 00:12:54.416
What about Marquis Taiping?

00:12:54.708 --> 00:12:56.958
Marquis Taiping made
such a huge fool of himself

00:12:57.166 --> 00:12:59.208
that His Majesty has reprimanded him.

00:12:59.500 --> 00:13:01.583
He has returned home to reflect.

00:13:03.125 --> 00:13:06.041
Shen Bingfan is promoted
to Chief Squad Leader for her service.

00:13:06.583 --> 00:13:07.500
Hua Mange

00:13:08.333 --> 00:13:10.750
will receive 3 commendations on record.

00:13:11.583 --> 00:13:12.041
And

00:13:12.250 --> 00:13:13.083
Cheng Xintian

00:13:13.625 --> 00:13:16.666
is exceptionally promoted
to seventh-rank Squad Leader.

00:13:17.041 --> 00:13:18.000
And each of you

00:13:18.166 --> 00:13:20.708
will be rewarded with 20 taels.

00:13:22.750 --> 00:13:24.250
Thank you, Commander.

00:13:32.750 --> 00:13:33.583
Shen Bingfan.

00:13:34.458 --> 00:13:36.083
Among all those under my command,

00:13:36.583 --> 00:13:38.916
you are the fastest to be promoted
to Chief Squad Leader.

00:13:39.416 --> 00:13:40.000
Remember.

00:13:40.583 --> 00:13:41.375
You must

00:13:41.916 --> 00:13:42.708
carry this honor

00:13:43.583 --> 00:13:44.458
forward.

00:13:45.708 --> 00:13:46.541
I will devote myself

00:13:46.708 --> 00:13:47.416
until my dying breath.

00:13:50.625 --> 00:13:51.208
My lord.

00:13:52.583 --> 00:13:53.875
In capturing Diaotu,

00:13:54.500 --> 00:13:56.750
Xu Duoyu found
the fragrance powder clue.

00:14:00.541 --> 00:14:02.041
Xu Duoyu has always wanted
to become a Jinyiwei.

00:14:02.375 --> 00:14:03.416
Please grant him that wish.

00:14:12.291 --> 00:14:14.375
Thank you, Shen and Hua,
for thinking highly of me.

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:16.666
But I think being a servant

00:14:17.375 --> 00:14:18.291
is good enough.

00:14:19.000 --> 00:14:19.458
Very well.

00:14:20.500 --> 00:14:21.583
In that case,

00:14:22.083 --> 00:14:25.208
Xu Duoyu will also receive 20 taels.

00:14:28.958 --> 00:14:30.041
Thank you, Commander.

00:14:30.310 --> 00:14:32.430
(Northern Bureau)

00:14:32.958 --> 00:14:33.500
Bingfan.

00:14:34.083 --> 00:14:35.583
Congratulations on becoming
Chief Squad Leader.

00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:36.750
I prepared a little wine

00:14:36.791 --> 00:14:37.666
to celebrate for you.

00:14:38.333 --> 00:14:39.083
A little wine?

00:14:39.916 --> 00:14:41.375
How little are we talking?

00:14:41.750 --> 00:14:42.416
Exactly.

00:14:42.500 --> 00:14:43.916
We were promoted and rewarded too.

00:14:44.041 --> 00:14:45.333
Why not treat us as well?

00:14:46.625 --> 00:14:47.333
All right.

00:14:47.500 --> 00:14:48.833
I can celebrate for you two as well.

00:14:49.208 --> 00:14:51.208
So we are just an afterthought?

00:14:52.875 --> 00:14:55.416
Then we'd better stay out of it.

00:14:56.125 --> 00:14:57.625
Otherwise, someone might say

00:14:57.625 --> 00:14:59.625
we can't take a hint.

00:15:00.166 --> 00:15:00.791
Agreed.

00:15:02.458 --> 00:15:03.125
Please go.

00:15:07.750 --> 00:15:10.000
Bingfan, did I say
the wrong thing again?

00:15:10.458 --> 00:15:12.625
Guan, I appreciate the thought.

00:15:13.083 --> 00:15:14.083
But I'll pass today.

00:15:15.041 --> 00:15:15.666
Why?

00:15:16.958 --> 00:15:19.208
Do you think my food and wine

00:15:19.208 --> 00:15:20.250
are not as good as Chong'er Pavilion's?

00:15:20.250 --> 00:15:21.041
No, not like that.

00:15:22.125 --> 00:15:25.208
I'm simply not in the mood
to drink today.

00:15:25.625 --> 00:15:26.166
I'm sorry.

00:15:27.458 --> 00:15:27.833
Bing...

00:15:32.375 --> 00:15:33.625
You were promoted
to Chief Squad Leader today.

00:15:33.916 --> 00:15:35.625
But I didn't see you celebrating
with Hua.

00:15:36.458 --> 00:15:37.333
Are you upset?

00:15:38.958 --> 00:15:39.458
Young Master Chang.

00:15:39.958 --> 00:15:41.791
Do you know the people
at the Northern Bureau well?

00:15:42.666 --> 00:15:43.250
Well enough.

00:15:43.500 --> 00:15:44.583
Then what kind of man

00:15:44.750 --> 00:15:45.583
do you think Lu Guokai is?

00:15:46.250 --> 00:15:46.875
Why?

00:15:49.416 --> 00:15:51.666
I was happy to be promoted
to Chief Squad Leader today.

00:15:52.541 --> 00:15:54.791
I thought, without the Commander,

00:15:55.041 --> 00:15:56.166
I wouldn't be where I am now.

00:15:56.958 --> 00:15:57.875
So after lunch,

00:15:58.583 --> 00:15:59.500
I wanted to thank him

00:15:59.500 --> 00:16:01.000
in person.

00:16:02.250 --> 00:16:03.000
(Stern and Dignified)
(My lord.)

00:16:03.000 --> 00:16:04.791
(Stern and Dignified)
(Diaotu has been sentenced to death.)

00:16:05.125 --> 00:16:07.166
(His case file will soon
be recorded and sealed.)

00:16:08.125 --> 00:16:08.916
(I believe)

00:16:09.625 --> 00:16:10.500
(before it's sealed,)

00:16:10.625 --> 00:16:12.416
(perhaps we should make a slight change)

00:16:13.083 --> 00:16:13.875
(to his file.)

00:16:14.375 --> 00:16:15.250
(What kind of change?)

00:16:15.291 --> 00:16:16.166
(I will sit down and explain.)

00:16:17.500 --> 00:16:18.916
(Say it now.)

00:16:25.708 --> 00:16:26.208
(My lord.)

00:16:37.500 --> 00:16:38.291
(The court)

00:16:39.000 --> 00:16:40.416
(doesn't approve of us
using female Jinyiwei.)

00:16:41.291 --> 00:16:41.916
(So)

00:16:42.333 --> 00:16:43.625
(in Diaotu's capture,)

00:16:43.916 --> 00:16:45.416
(we shouldn't mention
the female Jinyiwei.)

00:16:45.875 --> 00:16:47.000
(Then keep it vague.)

00:16:47.666 --> 00:16:50.833
(Don't say female Jinyiwei.
Just say Jinyiwei.)

00:16:52.500 --> 00:16:53.125
(Also,)

00:16:54.708 --> 00:16:57.291
(if we record that Diaotu hid inside
Marquis Taiping's manor,)

00:16:57.708 --> 00:16:58.916
(if that goes into the file,)

00:16:59.375 --> 00:16:59.875
(then)

00:17:00.333 --> 00:17:02.333
(Marquis Taiping will lose all face.)

00:17:03.125 --> 00:17:05.583
(After all, he is a first-rank marquis.)

00:17:08.333 --> 00:17:09.541
(I have an idea.)

00:17:09.875 --> 00:17:10.958
(Why not change it to this?)

00:17:11.750 --> 00:17:13.583
("While we were pursuing Diaotu,)

00:17:14.125 --> 00:17:15.666
(the criminal, with nowhere to run,)

00:17:16.125 --> 00:17:17.333
(fled into the marquis's manor)

00:17:17.666 --> 00:17:20.333
(and killed the maid Chunhong.)

00:17:21.208 --> 00:17:23.250
(The Jinyiwei then entered
and captured him.")

00:17:24.041 --> 00:17:26.083
(That protects
the Yin family's reputation)

00:17:27.250 --> 00:17:30.333
(and makes Marquis Taiping's manor
owe us a favor.)

00:17:32.333 --> 00:17:33.333
(Then do as you suggest.)

00:17:35.208 --> 00:17:36.958
Even in such a small case,

00:17:37.458 --> 00:17:39.375
Lu Guokai went to great lengths
to alter the truth.

00:17:40.916 --> 00:17:41.333
Tell me...

00:17:41.333 --> 00:17:41.916
So,

00:17:42.541 --> 00:17:44.333
you think he had something
to do with your father's case.

00:17:45.458 --> 00:17:45.916
Bingfan.

00:17:46.333 --> 00:17:47.166
In officialdom,

00:17:47.375 --> 00:17:49.041
many things can't be judged
by appearances.

00:17:49.875 --> 00:17:51.000
Take Diaotu's case.

00:17:51.333 --> 00:17:52.583
Who would have guessed that a predator

00:17:52.708 --> 00:17:54.375
was a villain who liked
disguising himself as a woman?

00:17:54.791 --> 00:17:55.833
If the fragrance powder
had not exposed him,

00:17:56.083 --> 00:17:57.166
how could you have caught him?

00:17:58.916 --> 00:18:00.750
But Lu Guokai is suspicious.

00:18:02.041 --> 00:18:03.708
From what I know of him,

00:18:04.083 --> 00:18:06.041
Lu Guokai has no powerful backing,

00:18:06.333 --> 00:18:07.708
but he craves fame and status.

00:18:08.000 --> 00:18:09.958
People like him are timid
and afraid of trouble.

00:18:10.208 --> 00:18:11.875
They know that if anything goes wrong,

00:18:12.125 --> 00:18:13.000
they have no one to protect them.

00:18:13.166 --> 00:18:15.250
So they tread carefully
and plan every step.

00:18:15.500 --> 00:18:16.041
That kind of man

00:18:16.916 --> 00:18:17.833
is not suited to be a mole.

00:18:19.750 --> 00:18:20.750
But I still don't trust him.

00:18:37.020 --> 00:18:40.190
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

00:18:40.560 --> 00:18:43.940
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

00:18:44.190 --> 00:18:47.190
♪My heart drifted lost♪

00:18:47.190 --> 00:18:50.600
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

00:18:51.690 --> 00:18:54.900
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

00:18:55.310 --> 00:18:58.650
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

00:18:59.230 --> 00:19:01.440
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

00:19:01.440 --> 00:19:05.480
♪I've softly let it go♪

00:19:05.480 --> 00:19:09.350
♪The vow you made was true♪

00:19:09.350 --> 00:19:13.100
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

00:19:13.400 --> 00:19:15.310
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

00:19:15.310 --> 00:19:19.850
♪And forget at world's end♪

00:19:20.150 --> 00:19:21.650
♪Embracing memory♪

00:19:21.650 --> 00:19:24.020
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

00:19:24.020 --> 00:19:27.900
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

00:19:27.900 --> 00:19:30.230
♪I wish to let it pass♪

00:19:30.230 --> 00:19:35.230
♪And run toward this vast life♪